</ul>

 <h3 class="text-light">> Industrial Accidents</h3>
<ul class="text-light">
    <li> Follow safety drills and wear appropriate protective equipment.</li>
<li>Report unsafe conditions immediately.</li>
<li>Train workers in emergency first aid and evacuation techniques.</li>
</ul>
<h3 class="text-light">> Health Emergencies</h3>
<ul class="text-light">
<li> Practice good hygiene: handwashing, sanitizing, etc.</li>
<li>Wear masks in public places if airborne transmission is a risk.</li>
<li> Keep basic medicines and health kits at home.</li>
</ul>

 
